name: OneTwentyPowerConverter
0:
”Alexa, open one twenty power converter”
”Alexa, ask one twenty power converter to compute how many watts is forty amps”

This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: one twenty power converter
des: In the United States most household electricity is at 120 volts. Now you can convert with the magic of Alexa amperage values to wattage as well as wattage to amperage.
